data.description: Fall in LOVE with this 4 Bedroom/2 Bath Open Concept Home in the Heart of Redland close to both Award Winning Redland Elementary & Middle Schools!  The Great Room features Soaring Ceilings, a Custom Barn Door, Cozy Fireplace with Gas Starter and a stunning Stone Surround and Custom Mantel, The Kitchen, a Culinary Delight, is equipped with Custom Cabinets, a versatile Work Island with Countertop Seating, Luxurious Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel appliances PLUS a HUGE Walk-In Pantry! It's a space designed to inspire your Inner Chef! The Master Suite is Serene, offering a Spacious Bedroom, His & Her Walk-In Closets, and an Ensuite Bathroom with Garden Tub, a HUGE Walk-In Shower, additional Linen Storage, separate Water Closet and Dual Vanity Areas, ensuring a spa-like experience every day. On the opposite side of the home enjoy three additional Spacious Bedrooms with Extra Storage plus an additional Hall Closet for Storage. The second Full Bath features a Double Vanity, Large Bath/Shower and additional Linen Closet. Step outside to the Covered Patio featuring a Fireplace and Connections for TV and Entertainment Systems. This property boasts a fully Fenced Backyard over-looking a lush Wooded Back Drop and Neighboring Horse Farm offering unparalleled privacy and serene views! The Over-Sized Back Yard features an Above-Ground Pool with Pump PLUS a Large Workshop for hobbies or storage! Just outside the back gate the owners have created a fire pit perfect for roasting marshmallows on cool evenings. Drop Everything as you enter this Incredible Home through the garage and keep it ALL organized in the Mud Room with Built In Shelving and Cabinets. Love to Rock Climb? Enjoy you're very own Custom Rock Wall in the Garage offering hours of Entertainment! Did I mention the tankless Hot Water Heater and Foam Insulation in the Attic offering Energy Efficient savings? You do not want to miss this Beautiful Home! Schedule Your Showing Today! Eligible for Zero Down USDA Loans.
